title: Orbit space
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Consider a group action of $$G$$ on a topological space $$X$$ by homeomorphism. We define the orbit space $$X/G$$ as the quotient $$X/\!\sim,$$ where $$x \sim y$$ if and only if there is a $$g \in G$$ such that $$y = g \cdot x.$$